<br />
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Aptos,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif">Please see below request for travel arrangements for NURSENAME at FACILITYNAME arriving/departing on DATE:</span></span></span><br />
<br />
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Aptos,sans-serif"><b>Please complete and return the table below with your travel arrangements within 24 hours of receiving this email</b>. Failure to provide this information promptly may result in a delay to the start date of your agency staff.</span></span></p>

