<p><br />
<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Aptos,sans-serif"><b><span style="background:yellow">Hunter New England LHD will handle all flight bookings. Nurses or the Agency Company are not permitted to make bookings under any circumstances. Flight details will be provided shortly.</span></b></span></span><br />
